    <innerclass refid="classiceberg_1_1ArrowRowBuilder" prot="public">iceberg::ArrowRowBuilder</innerclass>
    <innernamespace refid="namespaceiceberg">iceberg</innernamespace>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Internal Arrow row-building utilities shared by metadata tables.</para>
<para>Metadata tables (snapshots, history, manifests, ...) materialize in-memory structures into Arrow batches that conform to the table&apos;s Iceberg schema. <computeroutput>ArrowRowBuilder</computeroutput> wraps a nanoarrow <computeroutput><ref refid="structArrowArray" kindref="compound">ArrowArray</ref></computeroutput> initialized from such a schema and exposes per-column access plus typed append helpers so each metadata table can emit rows without re-implementing the nanoarrow boilerplate. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
